About the job

Mid-level React Developer - React, JavaScript, Typescript, HTML / CSS

Remote (UK)

£45,000 per year


I am working with an exciting SaaS company based in London who are looking for a passionate and enthusiastic Mid-level React Developer to join their team on a permanent basis.


My client are an innovative and forward thinking tech company that pride themselves on having a collaborative and welcoming culture. They are looking for a mid-level developer who has the desire to work in cross functional teams and upskill themselves.


You will be focused on the development of the user interface of their SaaS platform which is trusted by over 200 organisations using React, Typescript, Javascript, HTML and CSS.


They are offering:
  • Salary up to £45,000
  • Remote working
  • Project focused role
  • Strong mentorship culture
  • Uncapped personal training budgets
  • Regular learning workshops


What they are looking for:
  • 4+ years of experience working with React, JavaScript and Typescript
  • Exposure to automated testing tools and frameworks (e.g. Jest, Playwright)
  • Experience with git and deployment workflows
  • Proactive approach to work
  • Excellent communication and problem-solving skills


To learn more about the company and the position - apply now!!
